how to not get proxmox firewall to not block all lxc traffic:
1. Check iptable rules, if masquerading/
iptables -t nat -L POSTROUTING -v -n --line-numbers

2. delete rule
iptables -t nat -D POSTROUTING -j MASQUERADE

3. 
iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s 10.0.0.0/24 -o eno1 -j MASQUERADE

4. edit /etc/network/interfaces on host and add to bridge interface
post-up   iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -s '10.0.0.0/24' -o eno1 -j MASQUERADE
post-down iptables -t nat -D POSTROUTING -s '10.0.0.0/24' -o eno1 -j MASQUERADEpost-up   
